대사: @Dave How are you?@
@It's always the same for me.@
@What's the big news?@
@Hmm... Two small ones would be enough to make me remember...@★③☆①
@By the way^ I heard that smuggling crackdowns have intensified recently...@
@Is that it?@
@Two small ones if you want to hear more^ you know.@★③☆①
@I've noticed a lot of new faces in the slums lately.@
@A new face?@
@I'm having a hard time placing them.@★③☆①
@Now that I think about it^ I've smelled a strange ⓡ(●1ⓕfishy smell)ⓦ while walking around.@
@ⓡ(fishy smell)ⓦ?@
(He shrugged when I looked at him like this was a no-brainer.)
@Oddly enough^ it smells like that in places where it shouldn't...@★③☆①
@I hear there's a flea market coming up next to the north baker street.@
@I see...@★③☆①
@There have been many ships at the ⓑ(wharf)ⓦ recently. If it's not nighttime^ we can work anytime.@
@I see^ How much do they pay for it?@
@hey said they would give at least 3 dollars.@★③☆①
@The way things are going^ it looks like food prices are going to go up in the next month or so.@
@I'll have to stock up on something.@★③☆①
@Hmm... hold on a second.@
@Give me a couple more and I'll think about it.@★③☆①
@Hmmm... Speaking of which^ there's been a lot of talk lately about ⓡ(●1ⓢalligators in the sewers)ⓦ.@
@Is there alligators in the sewer?@
@It's just an ghost story^ after all. They say a wealthy person released the alligators they were raising to avoid getting caught.@
@And that alligators survived and now lives in the sewer... It's an incredible story^ isn't it?@
@I see...@
@I've never seen it^ although some people have said they've actually seen it.@★③☆①
@Two small ones.@★③☆①
@You're out of money.@
@There's nothing more I can tell you.@
@Uh^ have you heard about the ⓡ(●1ⓕfishy smell)ⓦ that's been going around lately?@
@Somehow^ I found the source of it.@
@It was the smell of ⓖ(●3ⓦsewer workers)ⓦ.@
@I suppose it might smell like that in there.@
@If you want to know more^ you can go to the ⓑ(●1ⓢsewage office)ⓦ. They were wearing clothes there.@★③☆①
@Hi ⓖ(Dave)ⓦ. I was wondering if you could do me a favor?@
